        "interactionId": "6ba60736-4e16-5a61-9f3b-c4b3f3970723",
        "speaker": "agent",
        "sequenceIndex": 47,
        "text": "My pleasure. Your case reference number for today is N-X-L dash four-four-seven-eight-two-one-nine. After we hang up, you'll receive a brief survey — if you have a moment to share your feedback, we'd really appreciate it.",
