        "interactionId": "98834515-c16b-58f2-9b5a-f3d8ecdfb139",
        "speaker": "agent",
        "sequenceIndex": 51,
        "text": "Your case reference number is N-X-L dash zero-four-seven-zero-one-nine-two. After we hang up you'll receive a brief survey — if you have a moment to share your feedback, we'd really appreciate it. Take care of yourself, Ms. Holloway. We'll be in touch very soon.",
