        "interactionId": "b1976505-57e4-5f6f-aa29-9f6bc4716757",
        "speaker": "agent",
        "sequenceIndex": 20,
        "text": "Honestly, the five-hundred plan tends to be the sweet spot for households like yours. It handles simultaneous four-K streams and video calls comfortably without paying for headroom you wouldn't use. Gigabit is real, but most households don't saturate it.",
        "startTime": 165.7,
