        "speaker": "agent",
        "sequenceIndex": 32,
        "text": "I'm not going to quote you a number I can't authorize. What I'm going to do is open a Manager Approval ticket for the full reversal — that's what the policy requires for amounts over my cap. You will receive an outcome within one business day.",
