        "id": "52459c06-d1c3-5164-96fc-edc54bfd3fa1",
        "interactionId": "204f6ce9-2307-56ca-ae61-1110269449ff",
        "speaker": "agent",
        "sequenceIndex": 18,
        "text": "That's the part I need to be transparent with you about. For a service credit based on speed, our refund policy specifically requires the evidence to come from a hardwired ethernet test, not WiFi.",
