        "interactionId": "204f6ce9-2307-56ca-ae61-1110269449ff",
        "speaker": "agent",
        "sequenceIndex": 20,
        "text": "I hear how that sounds, and the reason is real even if it's frustrating. WiFi adds variables we can't measure or fix from the network side — distance from the router, walls, neighbours' networks on the same channel, the device's own radio quality.",
