        "interactionId": "204f6ce9-2307-56ca-ae61-1110269449ff",
        "speaker": "agent",
        "sequenceIndex": 24,
        "text": "That's the right move. I'd rather do this together right now than have you go away guessing. Do you have a laptop or desktop computer with an ethernet port?",
