        "interactionId": "204f6ce9-2307-56ca-ae61-1110269449ff",
        "speaker": "agent",
        "sequenceIndex": 26,
        "text": "Perfect. So plug one end of that ethernet cable into the back of the router, into any of the yellow LAN ports, and the other end directly into your laptop. Turn the WiFi off on the laptop so we know we're testing the wired line and not falling back to WiFi.",
        "startTime": 223.96,
