        "interactionId": "204f6ce9-2307-56ca-ae61-1110269449ff",
        "speaker": "agent",
        "sequenceIndex": 38,
        "text": "It's a five dollar per month equipment line on the bill, no upfront. Or you can buy a third-party one and use it with our network — your choice. Either works.",
        "startTime": 326.83,
        "endTime": 334.11,
        "timestamp": "05:26",
