        "text": "That's right. Because the hardwired test confirmed the line is doing what you pay for, there isn't a service credit available in this case. I know that's not the answer you wanted, but I'd rather give you the real picture than apply a credit that wouldn't actually fix the experience.",
        "startTime": 342.76,
