        "interactionId": "47b132fa-82d8-51e1-b3b9-f4a7c7081cd6",
        "speaker": "agent",
        "sequenceIndex": 3,
        "text": "Ms. Caldwell, I am so sorry. Waiting a full morning for an appointment that doesn't show is genuinely frustrating, and I completely understand why you're upset.",
