        "interactionId": "47b132fa-82d8-51e1-b3b9-f4a7c7081cd6",
        "speaker": "agent",
        "sequenceIndex": 42,
        "text": "To summarize: today's eight to noon technician appointment was missed because of an internal reassignment with no customer notification, I've applied a twenty-five dollar account credit, I've rebooked you for Tuesday nine to eleven AM with priority flagged, and dispatch will confirm within four hours. Does that all sound right?",
