        "interactionId": "9f3735a4-db67-5112-8602-fa61caf25536",
        "speaker": "agent",
        "sequenceIndex": 38,
        "text": "Three — if you use a password manager, change the master password on it. If you reuse a password anywhere, change those individual accounts too, especially anything financial. The Data Compliance team will give you specific guidance based on what they find, but those three are the safe starting point now.",
        "startTime": 325.43,
