        "interactionId": "9f3735a4-db67-5112-8602-fa61caf25536",
        "speaker": "agent",
        "sequenceIndex": 40,
        "text": "Good. And one more thing — because the account is frozen, I'm not making any other changes today, and I want you to know that's deliberate. Even simple things like updating your billing address or the payment method are held until the freeze is lifted, exactly so a bad actor can't use a support call to do further damage.",
