        "interactionId": "9f3735a4-db67-5112-8602-fa61caf25536",
        "speaker": "agent",
        "sequenceIndex": 42,
        "text": "I'm sorry this is the situation you're dealing with today. You did the right thing by checking the activity and calling immediately — most accounts that get compromised, the customer doesn't notice for weeks.",
