        "interactionId": "9f3735a4-db67-5112-8602-fa61caf25536",
        "speaker": "agent",
        "sequenceIndex": 44,
        "text": "To summarize: you reported two suspicious sign-ins from a country you weren't in, I froze the account against all changes, flagged it as Security Review, opened a Data Compliance ticket which will follow up within seventy-two hours, and gave you three password changes to make on your side today. The freeze stays until Data Compliance lifts it. Does that all sound right?",
