        "speaker": "agent",
        "sequenceIndex": 16,
        "text": "It does. NexaLink processes deletion requests under both GDPR for European subjects and CCPA for California residents, and we apply the broader of the two protections regardless of which framework you cite — so whichever applies to you, the outcome is the same.",
