        "interactionId": "03b73e20-d3f0-5ffb-ab74-34f7657ee8f5",
        "speaker": "agent",
        "sequenceIndex": 20,
        "text": "Alright. So there are three categories I want to walk through, because they have different rules — and I think you'll want to know the distinction.",
