        "speaker": "agent",
        "sequenceIndex": 12,
        "text": "I can see you've been with us for almost four years, which is wonderful — and I can see your current plan is Home Pro Plus, the five hundred megabit plan, at seventy-nine dollars a month. Is that the bill that's creeping up?",
