        "speaker": "agent",
        "sequenceIndex": 26,
        "text": "Forty-four for the service, plus the eight dollar equipment fee, plus tax. So you'd be looking at roughly fifty-five to fifty-eight dollars total each month for the next twelve months, instead of close to ninety.",
        "startTime": 216.25,
        "endTime": 225.18,
